videos.description: Texas' Royce Hamm Jr. cleans up his teammate's early miss with a one-handed putback slam early vs. Georgetown.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Hamm cleans up with one-handed putback) 2019/11/21

videos.headline: Hamm cleans up with one-handed putback

videos.description: Brooklyn Net and former Texas Longhorn Kevin Durant sits courtside of the Texas vs. Georgetown college basketball game on Thursday night at Madison Square Garden.

videos.headline: Durant takes in Texas vs. Georgetown at MSG

videos.description: Kai Jones sticks with it and rises up for a two-handed slam to give Texas its biggest lead of the game vs. Georgetown.
